  "text": "We should emphasize, however, that openness to experience as a personality trait did not show association to the bipolar disorder phenotype in our current study sample [CITATION_1] . Therefore, although these findings for the openness trait may be of importance in identifying the genetic contribution to openness, in our sample, it may have limited relevance with regard to identifying genetic sites contributing in some way to the bipolar phenotype.",
